additional_chart_value_files:
global:
  enableUniqueDomainAsPrimary: false
  region: us-gov-west-1
  image:
    repository: 261727212250.dkr.ecr.us-gov-west-1.amazonaws.com/argoproj/argocd

projects:
  syncPolicy:
    automated:
      prune: true
      selfHeal: true
  targetRevision: master

apps:
  syncPolicy:
    automated:
      prune: true
      selfHeal: true
  targetRevision: master

argocd:
  enabled: true
  controller:
    args:
      selfHealTimeout: 30
    enableStatefulSet: false
  repoServer:
    extraContainers:
      - name: build-harness-cmp
        command: [ /var/run/argocd/argocd-cmp-server ] # Entrypoint should be Argo CD lightweight CMP server i.e. argocd-cmp-server
        image: 261727212250.dkr.ecr.us-gov-west-1.amazonaws.com/bip/build-harness:2022-01-14.1 # This can be off-the-shelf or custom built image
        securityContext:
          runAsNonRoot: true
          runAsUser: 999
        volumeMounts:
          - mountPath: /var/run/argocd
            name: var-files
          - mountPath: /home/argocd/cmp-server/plugins
            name: plugins
          - mountPath: /home/argocd/cmp-server/config/plugin.yaml # Plugin config file can either be volume mapped or baked into image
            subPath: plugin.yaml
            name: cmp-plugin
          - mountPath: /tmp
            name: tmp-dir
          - name: vault
            mountPath: /home/argocd/.vault_password
            subPath: vault-password
            readOnly: true
    volumes:
      - configMap:
          name: cmp-plugin
        name: cmp-plugin
      - name: vault
        secret:
          secretName: vault
          defaultMode: 0444
  server:
    volumeMounts:
      - name: certificate
        mountPath: /etc/ssl/certs/ca.crt # your self-signed CA part inside the secret
        subPath: rootCA
    volumes:
      - name: certificate
        configMap:
          name: argocd-cm
          defaultMode: 420
    configEnabled: false # Using our own config that can be templatized
    extraArgs:
      - --insecure
    additionalProjects:
      - name: argocd
        namespace: argocd
        additionalLabels: { }
        additionalAnnotations: { }
        description: Argocd Project
        sourceRepos:
          - '*'
        destinations:
          - namespace: argocd
            server: https://kubernetes.default.svc
        clusterResourceWhitelist:
          - group: '*'
            kind: '*'
        orphanedResources:
          warn: false
    config:
      admin.enabled: "true"
      url: https://argocd.{{ include "argocd-bootstrap.primary_domain" . }}
      resource.customizations: |
        argoproj.io/Application:
          health.lua: |
            hs = {}
            hs.status = "Progressing"
            hs.message = ""
            if obj.status ~= nil then
              if obj.status.health ~= nil then
                hs.status = obj.status.health.status
                if obj.status.health.message ~= nil then
                  hs.message = obj.status.health.message
                end
              end
            end
            return hs

        velero.io/BackupStorageLocation:
          health.lua: |
           hs = {}
           hs.status = "Progressing"
           hs.message = ""
           if obj.status ~= nil then
             if obj.status.phase ~= nil and obj.status.phase == "Available" and obj.status.lastSyncedTime ~= nil then
               hs.status = "Healthy"
             return hs
             end
           end
           return hs
  dex:
    enabled: false
  redis:
    image:
      repository: "261727212250.dkr.ecr.us-gov-west-1.amazonaws.com/redis"
  redis-ha: #This is an odditiy of helm in that dependencies switching is at the top level, but it still may need to reference in the template as well
    enabled: false
  applicationSet:
    enabled: false
  notifications:
    enabled: false
redis-ha: #This is an odditiy of helm in that dependencies switching is at the top level, but it still may need to reference in the template as well
  enabled: false
global:
  deployEnv: dev
  legacyEnv: dev8
  domains:
    standard: dev.bip.va.gov
    legacy: dev8.bip.va.gov

projects:
  targetRevision: 1.5.1

apps:
  targetRevision: 1.5.1
